==English==
===Etymology===
From Greek ''huperboreas''

===Proper noun===
'''Hyperborea'''
#''(Greek mythology)'' The land of sunshine and plenty, beyond the northern wind.
#'' (metaphorical)'' The extreme north of the Earth; an area in a northerly region.

